We have so many agents to make it work

10:13.875 --> 10:19.333
to make it work and work very hard.

10:19.792 --> 10:23.125
You know what is in second chakra.

10:24.792 --> 10:30.417
In the second chakra what happens

10:31.667 --> 10:35.875
that we are caught up by our ambition

10:37.875 --> 10:41.417
