10:41.667 --> 10:47.333
and I've seen many Sahaja Yogis also getting lost,

10:47.583 --> 10:52.875
so it's a very important day for all of you.

10:58.583 --> 11:01.667
So second chakra is important because

11:02.041 --> 11:06.041
in modern times it is very, very

11:06.333 --> 11:10.792
cosmic as well as active.

11:13.125 --> 11:15.709
