11:49.333 --> 11:53.041
who is angry, all sorts of nonsense.

11:55.333 --> 11:57.458
You are all Sahaja yogis,

11:58.583 --> 12:01.709
so you shouldn't worry as to all these people,

12:02.041 --> 12:03.709
what they say, what they are doing.

12:04.041 --> 12:08.250
You should just enjoy yourself.

12:08.542 --> 12:11.709
Second chakra you must enjoy.

12:12.041 --> 12:15.792
That's the best way to enjoy Sahaja Yoga.

12:19.917 --> 12:22.917
Where your Swadisthana is satisfied

12:24.250 --> 12:28.542
nothing can destroy you or disturb you.

12:29.458 --> 12:33.542
At Swadisthana you can really look after;

12:33.792 --> 12:39.208
Swadisthan Chakra is so much good for you because

12:39.542 --> 12:44.625
now you are Sahaja Yogis and you can master it.

12:44.917 --> 12:50.041
That is one chakra which upsets, especially in the West

12:50.333 --> 12:52.542
people think too much, all the time

12:52.792 --> 12:54.625
thinking, thinking, thinking.

12:56.333 --> 12:58.333
That's from Swadisthan,

12:58.625 --> 13:03.041
you get that problem from Swadisthan.

13:04.333 --> 13:08.917
To satisfy Swadisthan, you have to take to silence.

13:10.250 --> 13:17.709
You have to take to quietude and look at yourself.

13:18.041 --> 13:24.166
What is bothering you, what is troubling you,

13:24.458 --> 13:27.542
what gives you ideas and thoughts

13:27.834 --> 13:30.041
is Swadisthan.

13:30.375 --> 13:33.041
And some people think so much.

13:36.375 --> 13:39.542
There may not be any problem,

13:39.834 --> 13:43.917
but they create their own problem with the Swadisthana

13:44.250 --> 13:49.458
and just go on bothering about the stuff.

13:49.709 --> 13:53.542
Swadisthan is very happy

13:53.834 --> 13:56.709
when you are just laughing and enjoying

13:57.083 --> 14:00.083
and not bothered about nonsense.

14:00.375 --> 14:03.959
How much time we waste on nonsense!

14:05.166 --> 14:06.917
We don't need it,

14:07.250 --> 14:09.458
Sahaja Yogis don't need it.

14:09.709 --> 14:13.375
It's only those who are not yet realized

14:13.667 --> 14:20.458
must be suffering. They do suffer
and they might even trouble you, but just laugh at it

14:20.709 --> 14:27.834
and you must pardon them, forgive them, because they are doing this

14:29.083 --> 14:33.250
because they can't help it.

14:34.583 --> 14:39.583
You see, this Swadisthan Chakra is bothering them

14:39.834 --> 14:41.375
so they can't help it.

