17:12.750 --> 17:14.583
you know in thousands they are,

17:14.834 --> 17:18.583
but nothing like Australian, I see.

17:19.834 --> 17:26.750
Because they are somehow or other very deeply touched

17:27.083 --> 17:31.667
and bothered about the world problems.

17:33.917 --> 17:35.917
So what you have to think now:

17:36.291 --> 17:40.208
not to have anything to do with Swadisthan,

17:40.583 --> 17:43.500
but what you have to become

17:43.750 --> 17:46.667
is you are Sahaja Yogis

17:48.000 --> 17:51.750
and no Swadisthan should bother you.

